OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmainly cloudy evening with some patchy
OL,7,Flight rain. This dying out tonight
OL,8,Fwith some clear spells developing
OL,9,Falong with some mist or low cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FAny low cloud burning off to
OL,12,Fleave a dry bright day with some sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Very warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,16,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm.
OL,17,FSunny, hot inland Thursday, coastal
OL,18,Fhaar, perhaps some thundery showers
OL,19,Flater. Showery on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
